HEADWORD: Pertused
<hw>Per*tused"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>
}</mhw>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L. <ets>pertusus</ets>, p. p. of
<ets>pertundere</ets> to beat or thrust through, to bore through;
